      <title>美国监管机构警告信用卡发行商不要降低奖励价值</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-watchdog-warns-credit-card-issuers-not-devalue-rewards-2024-12-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高消费者金融监管机构周三警告称，信用卡公司降低或取消持卡人赚取的奖励积分、现金返还或里程可能违法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-watchdog-warns-credit-card-issuers-not-devalue-rewards-2024-12-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 10:05:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>二十国集团监督机构敦促各国政府解决非银行金融风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/g20-watchdog-urges-governments-address-non-bank-financial-risks-2024-12-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融稳定理事会（FSB）周三向各国政府提出建议，降低对冲基金、保险公司和其他非银行金融中介机构的风险，这些机构目前占全球金融资产的近一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/g20-watchdog-urges-governments-address-non-bank-financial-risks-2024-12-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 09:04:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长温施表示，欧元走弱可能会减轻美国关税的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/ecbs-wunsch-says-euro-parity-may-cushion-impact-new-tariffs-2024-12-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行政策制定者皮埃尔·温施周三对路透社表示，欧元贬值至与美元平价将缓解美国新关税对欧元区经济增长的影响，尽管这将推高通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/ecbs-wunsch-says-euro-parity-may-cushion-impact-new-tariffs-2024-12-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 08:06:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
